nodes.text: Reena University was a university in the galaxy. During the Separatist Crisis, Count Dooku, leader of the Independent Movement for Self-Determination, was set to give a series of presentations in the university's Panos Lecture Hall, called the Reena University Lecture Series, which Reena University student government official Ansibella Dellu began making a poster advertising, entitled Count Dooku: Words of Truth.
